{"tid":2504621,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「快必」被控發表煽動文字等罪 申請永久終止聆訊被駁回","createTime":"2021-04-26T04:17:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T14:14:34.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c86611921dcca7dd3e22639033d2d0e55cd04390","tid":2504621,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T04:17:07.000Z","msg":"人民力量副主席「快必」譚得志涉去年擺街站期間，多次高叫口號及派發政治宣傳單張，被控八項發表煽動文字罪等罪。他早前向法庭申請永久終止聆訊，陳廣池法官今在區域法院駁回申請。<br />\n<br />\n譚得志現共被控7項發表煽動文字、3項擾亂公眾秩序罪，以及各1項煽惑他人參與未經批准集結罪、舉行或召集一個未經批准公眾集結罪、拒絕遵從或故意忽略命令罪及串謀發表煽動文字罪。"},{"pid":"559a9be4ecd1940520de758860af94fd84e4b59e","tid":2504621,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T04:26:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />思想犯罪"},{"pid":"bffe57370efa628b8583b5ddbe882afaee7b9034","tid":2504621,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T04:34:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e64647b2ed6c7933d04cd7fe23cf2447c0c0103","tid":2504621,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T04:37:03.000Z","msg":"人民力量副主席譚得志涉嫌去年擺街站期間，多次高叫口號及派發政治宣傳單張，被控發表煽動文字罪等多項控罪，他早前向法庭申請永久終止聆訊，今日在區域法院被駁回。案件將如期在下月10日開審，並於下月3日先作審前覆核。<br />\n<br />\n法官陳廣池表示，法庭可下令中止案件的司法程序，但行使權力時必須符合特定情況，包括法庭認為案件不可能達致公平審訊，以及出現濫用司法程序情況，但這情況相當特殊。<br />\n<br />\n法官說，辯方不依賴濫用司法程序這議題，但未有證明審訊對被告構成不公，辯方主要爭議是指發表煽動文字罪與《基本法》及《人權法》牴觸，有關爭議應在正審提出，不應用作申請中止聆訊。<br />\n<br />\n另外，辯方要求控方提交更仔細的控罪詳情，列出被告哪一言行構成煽動罪，讓他確切知道自己所面對的指控，這項申請亦被駁回。法官說，控方除了依賴控罪詳情外，亦依賴案情摘要及涉案片段作證，從這些資料已清晰可知控方立場，沒有對被告構成不利。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1587725-20210426.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1587725-20210426.htm&d=D9q%2FqAhMrjKrs4nvjauepJLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=541057b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1587725-20210426.htm&h=19e8c804\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1587725-20210426.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1bba907dcf3c4163ad4d69e7b6fde8c6e94b89cd","tid":2504621,"uid":260121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T04:37:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f374b6104c3c9a98013c9dc3d01d7762d5aa456","tid":2504621,"uid":110043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T04:42:14.000Z","msg":"黨安法狗官"},{"pid":"8550b27a0d6e46bfce6f49ba4fdc6275b75871dc","tid":2504621,"uid":52705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T04:44:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f76084bfa383deab6f403e01f62135793289ab4d","tid":2504621,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T05:24:59.000Z","msg":"未審先囚<br />\n<br />\n不知所謂<br />\n<br />\n垃撚圾"},{"pid":"97f791b44d9c7871f521ac847b22c64e1f3b648b","tid":2504621,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T05:42:24.000Z","msg":"人民力量副主席「快必」譚得志被控去年多次擺街站及遊行期間引發他人憎恨和藐視政府。他早前申請終止本案聆訊，質疑他面對的煽動罪用字含糊抽象，對言論自由構成不必要限制，違反《基本法》及人權法。區域法院法官陳廣池今裁決指，控罪是否違憲，應該留待正審才提出，認為辯方未能證明被告會如何遭受不公審訊，駁回辯方申請。案件將於下周一進行審前覆核，並如期於下月10日開審。<br />\n<br />\n控方回應指，質疑控罪違憲顯然並非申請終止聆訊的有力理由。如果控罪不符《基本法》，法庭有權作出補救性詮釋。若然控罪出現違憲爭議，大可留待審訊時再提出。<br />\n<br />\n控方又表示，控罪字眼的意思會隨著時間和地點有所改變，主審法官可以按情況自行詮釋。控方亦指，即使演講者無意煽動暴力，採取行動維護國家安全或公共秩序的做法，亦屬合乎比例。<br />\n<br />\n陳官裁決指，法庭有權行使酌情權終止案件聆訊，但門檻頗高，亦要符合若干情況，當中包括被吿不可能面對公平審訊、以及案件若然繼續檢控會構成濫用司法程序等。陳官指出，有關情況頗為特殊，辯方有責任證明被告會如何遭受不公平審訊。<br />\n<br />\n陳官表示，終止聆訊申請的重點，應為案件有否出現濫用司法程序的情況。質疑控罪違憲一事，應是審訊時提出的議題之一，並非在申請終止聆訊時提出。陳官認為辯方未能顯示被告如何有機會遭受不公審訊，亦未能證明被告面對的煽動罪有濫用程序之嫌，決定拒絕行使酌情權，不會中止案件聆訊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210426/4KMUJZJJJBEQNGVY3RHH4MNU5A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210426%2F4KMUJZJJJBEQNGVY3RHH4MNU5A%2F&d=D9q%2FqAhMrjKrs4nvjauepJLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=8854352c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210426%2F4KMUJZJJJBEQNGVY3RHH4MNU5A%2F&h=fe159446\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210426/4KMUJZJJJBEQNGVY3RHH4MNU5A/</a>"},{"pid":"1a96c88ee74f20f42d3d707aee11a66e685da9a5","tid":2504621,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T06:45:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82ae5973b80171361217580d621a50c151e71355","tid":2504621,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T06:51:34.000Z","msg":"必快<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32648f44ce3791bcb4097beef77d7b0843f2cf4a","tid":2504621,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T09:49:47.000Z","msg":"法官稱，就本案而言，辯方申請終止聆訊的唯一理據，是指煽動罪違憲。但法官指，控罪是否違憲，屬於審訊中其中一環，辯方不應該抽出來作終止聆訊的理據。辯方亦未能說服法庭，控罪違憲這點如何構成不公平審訊，以及繼續審訊會對被告不公，因為被告一共涉及 14 項控罪。辯方亦未能證明控方濫用程序。法官裁定，辯方申請終止聆訊的理據不成立，拒絕批出有關申請。<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E8%AD%9A%E5%BE%97%E5%BF%97%E5%B0%B1%E7%85%BD%E5%8B%95%E7%BD%AA%E7%94%B3%E7%B5%82%E6%AD%A2%E8%81%86%E8%A8%8A-%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%98%E9%99%B3%E5%BB%A3%E6%B1%A0%E6%8B%92%E7%B5%95-%E6%8C%87%E6%9C%AA%E8%83%BD%E8%AA%AA%E6%9C%8D%E6%B3%95%E5%BA%AD%E6%A7%8B%E6%88%90%E5%AF%A9%E8%A8%8A%E4%B8%8D%E5%85%AC/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%25AD%259A%25E5%25BE%2597%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E7%2585%25BD%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E7%2594%25B3%25E7%25B5%2582%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E8%2581%2586%25E8%25A8%258A-%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25AE%2598%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E6%25B1%25A0%25E6%258B%2592%25E7%25B5%2595-%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%259C%25AA%25E8%2583%25BD%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E6%259C%258D%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E6%25A7%258B%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E8%25A8%258A%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2585%25AC%2F&d=D9q%2FqAhMrjKrs4nvjauepJLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=4c49a958\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%25AD%259A%25E5%25BE%2597%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E7%2585%25BD%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E7%2594%25B3%25E7%25B5%2582%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E8%2581%2586%25E8%25A8%258A-%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25AE%2598%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E6%25B1%25A0%25E6%258B%2592%25E7%25B5%2595-%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%259C%25AA%25E8%2583%25BD%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E6%259C%258D%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E6%25A7%258B%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E8%25A8%258A%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2585%25AC%2F&h=3d66798a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E8%AD%9A%E5%BE%97%E5%BF%97%E5%B0%B1%E7%85%BD%E5%8B%95%E7%BD%AA%E7%94%B3%E7%B5%82%E6%AD%A2%E8%81%86%E8%A8%8A-%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%98%E9%99%B3%E5%BB%A3%E6%B1%A0%E6%8B%92%E7%B5%95-%E6%8C%87%E6%9C%AA%E8%83%BD%E8%AA%AA%E6%9C%8D%E6%B3%95%E5%BA%AD%E6%A7%8B%E6%88%90%E5%AF%A9%E8%A8%8A%E4%B8%8D%E5%85%AC/</a>"},{"pid":"cd9d521870c8f43cdc26756aa28dd27170c0d1ec","tid":2504621,"uid":363016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82ae5973b80171361217580d621a50c151e71355","tid":2504621,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T06:51:34.000Z","msg":"必快<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T09:51:30.000Z","msg":"連豬皮蛋粥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bca05b8b6124dfa7eb20935bfae97237829dc969","tid":2504621,"uid":191588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T09:51:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b8fa354f4c85610ea5e98193a2e222bb14afe4cc","tid":2504621,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd9d521870c8f43cdc26756aa28dd27170c0d1ec","tid":2504621,"uid":363016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82ae5973b80171361217580d621a50c151e71355","tid":2504621,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T06:51:34.000Z","msg":"必快<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T09:51:30.000Z","msg":"連豬皮蛋粥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T11:18:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e45ca75d9b42da3696e033c26048473dcbc19e7","tid":2504621,"uid":267488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T14:14:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}